Program: Omnibus
Title: Slaughter of the Innocents
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376jkr
Last Broadcast Date: 06 December 1988
Is there any truth to the story of the Massacre of the Innocents in Bethlehem as told by Matthew in the Bible's Old Testament?This programme traces the origins of the story and compares it with other historical accounts of the period.